snippet: Jose Altuve had four hits for the second straight night, Brad Peacock threw 6 1-3 solid innings and the Houston Astros beat the Los Angeles Angels 8-3 on Tuesday night....

headline.print_headline: Astros Win Again Behind Peacock and Altuve
headline.main: Astros Win Again Behind Peacock and Altuve

lead_paragraph: Jose Altuve had four hits for the second straight night, Brad Peacock threw 6 1-3 solid innings and the Houston Astros beat the Los Angeles Angels 8-3 on Tuesday night.
